div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-1 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/ww1\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01snhcq.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01snhcq\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Discover new perspectives on World War One</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-2 iwonder\n                    k-colour-palette-palette-2\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/guides/z38rq6f\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp square\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x256/p01l3r7h.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01l3r7h\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">History</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-header\">Has poetry distorted our view of World War One?</p></div><div class=\"connection\"><p class=\"k-type-body-index\"><img src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/80x80/p01lj3z7.jpg\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"type\">Presented by</span><span class=\"name\">Ian McMillan</span></p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-3 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-22887110\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01qhkg8.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01qhkg8\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite icon k-article\">Read</span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">History</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">BBC News: How accurately does Blackadder reflect history?</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-4 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01sm2k8\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01snqnf.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01snqnf\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Why George V declared a road in Manchester ‘England’s bravest street’</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-5 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/books/non_fictionreviews/3670201/Was-Field-Marshal-Haig-a-hero-or-dunderhead.html\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01qmbnr.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01qmbnr\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite icon k-link\">Visit</span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">History</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Was Field-Marshal Haig a hero or dunderhead?</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-6 iwonder\n                    k-colour-palette-palette-5\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/guides/zs9bwmn\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp square\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x256/p01q7zcp.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01q7zcp\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">History</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-header\">Why were journalists threatened with execution in WW1?</p></div><div class=\"connection\"><p class=\"k-type-body-index\"><img src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/80x80/p01q7zy7.jpg\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"type\">Presented by</span><span class=\"name\">Frank Gardner, BBC News</span></p></div></a></div></div></div></div></section><footer class=\"k-g-footer\"><div id=\"k-g-gn-footer\"><ol class=\"k-g-gn\"><li><a href=\"#z2x3wmn\">Lions led by donkeys</a></li><li><a href=\"#ztpc2hv\">The popular view of generals</a></li><li><a href=\"#zy3wpv4\">An unprecedented war</a></li><li><a href=\"#z3r7fg8\">The cost of being a British general i